    <item>
      <title>对贸易战争的担忧暴跌后的石油稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者评估了美国贸易政策的最新变化及其对中国需求的影响，这是全球最大的原油进口商，因此石油在本周进行了最大的下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 22:42:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票，债券下沉，因为美国 - 中国贸易吐口水加热：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在对中国的进一步关税张力引发了全球市场的新疾病之后，美国的股票和债券下跌，这些疾病蔓延到商品，货币和亚洲股票期货。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 22:39:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本股票将恢复在美中贸易紧张局势上滑动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/japanese-stocks-set-to-resume-slide-on-us-china-trade-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心世界上两个最大经济体之间的贸易战不断升级将减缓全球增长，因此日本股票将追踪其美国同行的幻灯片。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/japanese-stocks-set-to-resume-slide-on-us-china-trade-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 22:34:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税混乱是赚钱的，让华尔街飞翔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/tariff-chaos-comes-for-earnings-leaves-wall-street-flying-blind</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽·谢尔（Mari Shor）深入介绍了唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的关税对她在哥伦比亚螺纹公司（Columbia Threadneedle）分析的数十家消费者公司的意义，当时有人中断了她。同事说，玛丽（Mari）暂停了关税，您覆盖的股票飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/tariff-chaos-comes-for-earnings-leaves-wall-street-flying-blind</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 22:07:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
